          },
          "_name": "content1",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section article content1\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width Content\" name=\"widthContent\" min=\"1\" max=\"4\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-class=\"{'col-md-6': widthContent == 1, 'col-md-8': widthContent == 2, 'col-md-10': widthContent == 3, 'col-md-12': widthContent == 4}\"><p>Quantitive Survey - Results Highlights</p></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise4",
          "_cid": "s3vBDsKrX6",
          "_anchor": "content1-aj",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text, blockquote": {
              "color": "#767676"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#232323"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content1",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section article content1\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width Content\" name=\"widthContent\" min=\"1\" max=\"4\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-class=\"{'col-md-6': widthContent == 1, 'col-md-8': widthContent == 2, 'col-md-10': widthContent == 3, 'col-md-12': widthContent == 4}\"><p>Almost all the students who left a comment in the survey expressed<b> frustrations</b> with the current platforms and hope to have an app that combines all the features they use often.</p></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise4",
          "_cid": "s3vBDt33IN",
          "_anchor": "content1-ak",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#232323"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content3",
          "_customHTML": "<section mbr-id=\"_anchor\" mbr-paddings class=\"mbr-section article content3\">\n      \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) --> \n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width Content\" name=\"widthContent\" min=\"1\" max=\"4\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <select title=\"Cards\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->     \n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"row col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-md-6': widthContent == 1, 'col-md-8': widthContent == 2, 'col-md-10': widthContent == 3, 'col-md-12': widthContent == 4}\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-article data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-class=\"{'col-md-6': cardsAmount == 2, 'col-md-12': cardsAmount == 1, 'col-md-4': cardsAmount == 3}\">\n                     <p><b>Top “Crucial to include” Features :\n</b></p><p>1. Single sign-on (70%)\n</p><p>2. Chapel Attendance (56%)\n</p><p>3. Directory (53%)\n</p><p>4. Building and Service Hours (41%)\n</p><p>5. Emergency Contact (40%)\n</p><p>6. Class Schedules (39%)\n</p><p>7. Menu (37%)\n</p><p>8. Chapel Seat Map (27%)</p><p><br></p><p>\n</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-article data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-class=\"{'col-md-6': cardsAmount == 2, 'col-md-4': cardsAmount == 3}\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 1\">\n                     <p><b>Top percentages “Quite helpful” Features</b>:\n</p><p>1. Chapel Schedule (44%)\n</p><p>2. Building and Service Hours (43%)\n</p><p>3. Event (41%)\n</p><p>4. Announcement (40%)\n</p><p>5. Academic/Housing Calendar (37%)\n</p><p>6. Chapel Attendance (36%)\n</p><p>7. Menu (35%)\n</p><p>8. Class Schedules (34%)\n</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-md-4 mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-article data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\">\n                     <p>Make your own website in a few clicks! Mobirise helps you cut down development time by providing you with a flexible website editor with a drag and drop interface. Mobirise Website Builder creates responsive, retina and mobile friendly websites in a few clicks. Mobirise is one of the easiest website development tools available today. It also gives you the freedom to develop as many websites as you like given the fact that it is a desktop app.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "s3vBDtkiHJ",
          "_anchor": "content3-al",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "background": "@bgColor",
            ".media-container-row": {
              "margin": "0 auto",
              "align-items": "stretch",
              "-webkit-align-items": "stretch",
              ".img-item": {
                "display": "-webkit-flex",
                "flex-direction": "column",
                "justify-content": "center",
                "position": "relative",
                "width": "100%",
                "z-index": "1",
                "-webkit-flex-direction": "column",
                "-webkit-justify-content": "center",
                "img": {
                  "width": "100%",
                  "min-height": "1px"
                },
                ".img-caption": {
                  "background": "@cpBg",
                  "z-index": "2",
                  "padding": "1rem 1rem",
                  "word-break": "break-word",
                  "p": {
                    "margin-bottom": "0"
                  }
                },
                "&.item1": {
                  "padding": "0 2rem 0 0"
                }
              }
            },
            "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
              ".img-item": {
                "width": "100% !important",
                "&.item1": {
                  "width": "100%",
                  "flex-basis": "initial !important",
                  "padding": "0 0 2rem 0 !important",
                  "-webkit-flex-basis": "initial !important"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "content13",
          "_customHTML": "<section>\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width\" name=\"contentWidth\" min=\"66\" max=\"100\" value=\"84\" step=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Sizes\" name=\"proportions\" min=\"30\" max=\"300\" value=\"122\" step=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Caption\" name=\"showCaption\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Caption Background\" name=\"cpBg\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"media-container-row\" mbr-style=\"{'width':contentWidth+'%'}\">\n                <div class=\"img-item item1\" mbr-style=\"{'width':proportions+'%'}\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/survey-results-1-890x457.png\" alt title>\n                    <div class=\"img-caption\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-black\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            Question: “How much do you feel the need for a stand-alone Wheaton mobile app (in addition to the Student on Tap mobile website)?\n\n\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"img-item\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/survey-results-2-780x504.png\" alt title>\n                    <div class=\"img-caption\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-black\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            Question: “What's your opinion of the following functions of Student on Tap?”\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "s3vBDtG1fr",
          "_anchor": "content13-am",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".line": {
              "background-color": "@lineColor",
              "color": "@lineColor",
              "align": "center",
              "height": "2px",
              "margin": "0 auto"
            },
            ".section-text": {
