          },
          "_name": "content1",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section article content1\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width Content\" name=\"widthContent\" min=\"1\" max=\"4\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-class=\"{'col-md-6': widthContent == 1, 'col-md-8': widthContent == 2, 'col-md-10': widthContent == 3, 'col-md-12': widthContent == 4}\"><p><b>Usability Test – First Round</b></p></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise4",
          "_cid": "s3vE6qBOzU",
          "_anchor": "content1-i8",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text, blockquote": {
              "color": "#767676"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#232323"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content1",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section article content1\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width Content\" name=\"widthContent\" min=\"1\" max=\"4\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-text col-12 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-class=\"{'col-md-6': widthContent == 1, 'col-md-8': widthContent == 2, 'col-md-10': widthContent == 3, 'col-md-12': widthContent == 4}\"><p>I conducted 5 modulated usability tests (three in-person and two remote ones).</p><p><b>Objective:</b> Uncover usability problems in the existing red routes.</p><p><b>Result/Findings:</b></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">All the users were able to complete the tasks eventually, though some took a lot longer than the others due to the issues described below.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p>1. There was no major issue with the layout and navigation, though some menu items need to be reworded.</p><p>2. All of the users chose to login first. When I showed them the not logged in screens, they were able to notice the difference and login immediately.</p><p>3. Some of the users were confused about what \"Directory\" and \"Hours and Contact\" meant.</p><p>4. Many users didn't think about using the filter in the first place.</p><p>5. It was very easy to locate settings and \"my profile.\" Users like the multiple routes to complete the same task.</p><p>Here is the sample list of the issues by priority and before and after comparisons of the critical and major issues.</p><p><br></p></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise4",
          "_cid": "s3vE6qXNAP",
          "_anchor": "content1-i9",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "background": "@bgColor",
            "& when (@fullWidth = false)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)"
            },
            "& when (@gradientBg)": {
              "background": "linear-gradient(45deg, @bgColor, @color2)"
            },
            ".image-block": {
              "margin": "auto",
              "& when (@fullWidth)": {
                "width": "100% !important"
              }
            },
            "figcaption": {
              "position": "relative",
              "div": {
                "position": "absolute",
                "bottom": "0",
                "width": "100%"
              }
            },
            "@media (max-width: 768px)": {
              ".image-block": {
                "width": "100% !important"
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "image1",
          "_customHTML": "<section group=\"Images & Videos\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" value=\"0\" step=\"1\" condition=\"fullWidth==false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" value=\"0\" step=\"1\" condition=\"fullWidth==false\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\">        \n        \n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width\" name=\"imageSize\" min=\"20\" max=\"100\" value=\"66\" step=\"1\" condition=\"fullWidth==false\">\n\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"fullWidth==false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Gradient\" name=\"gradientBg\" condition=\"fullWidth==false\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color 2\" name=\"color2\" value=\"#149dcc\" condition=\"gradientBg && fullWidth==false\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <figure class=\"mbr-figure\" mbr-class=\"{'container':fullWidth==false}\">\n        <div class=\"image-block\" mbr-style=\"{'width':imageSize+'%'}\">\n            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/capstone-one-usability-test-template-1466x1897.jpg\" width=\"1400\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title>\n            <figcaption class=\"mbr-figure-caption mbr-figure-caption-over\" mbr-if=\"showText\">\n                <div mbr-text class=\"container pb-5 mbr-white align-center mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\">\n                    Create awesome websites!\n                </div>\n            </figcaption>\n        </div>\n    </figure>\n</section>",
